analysis.Summary: A Vue 3 component that renders an "unmute" (volume on) SVG icon with a customizable fill color.
analysis.Purpose: Provide a reusable icon component for unmuted audio state in the application's navigation or control panels.

Components.name: IconUnMute
Components.role: Renders an inline SVG representing a speaker with sound waves; accepts a "fill" prop to set the SVG color.

Functions.name: defineProps
Functions.description: Defines the component's props in the <script setup> block.

fill.description: Color used to fill the SVG path; defaults to the CSS variable --black.

Dependencies: CSS variables (specifically --black from the global style sheet)
Notes: There is no <style> block; all styling is handled via SVG attributes and CSS variables.
The default value for the `fill` prop is declared as an object rather than a stringâ€”this may be a typo or misconfiguration.
Uses inline SVG for crisp rendering at any size without external asset loading.
The component leverages Vue 3's <script setup> syntax for a minimal footprint.
